A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.com%2Fnews%2Farticles%2Fcz6p1g54q85o%230%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22A%20message%20appearing%20for%20US%20users%20said%20a%20law%20banning%20TikTok%20had%20been%20enacted%2C%20meaning%20%26quot%3Byou%20can't%20use%20TikTok%20for%20now%26quot%3B.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A332%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.com%2Fnews%2Farticles%2Fcz6p1g54q85o%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-bbc-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.bbc.com%2Fnews%2Farticles%2Fcz6p1g54q85o.amp%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.com%2Fnews%2Farticles%2Fcz6p1g54q85o.amp%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22TikTok%20Stops%20Working%20For%20US%20Users%20Ahead%20Of%20Federal%20Ban%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3ETikTok%20disconnected%20access%20to%20its%20users%20in%20the%20United%20States%20late%20Saturday%20shortly%20before%20a%20national%20ban%20on%20the%20app%20was%20to%20take%20effect%2C%20with%20President-elect%20Donald%20Trump%20unable%20to%20intervene%20until%20he%20takes%20office.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BA%20law%20banning%20TikTok%20has%20been%20enacted%20in%20the%20US%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20a%20message%20to%20users%20attempting%20to%20use%20the%20app.%20%26quot%3BUnfortunately%2C%20that%20means%20you%20can't%20use%20TikTok%20for%20now.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20are%20fortunate%20that%20President%20Trump%20has%20indicated%20that%20he%20will%20work%20with%20us%20on%20a%20solution%20to%20reinstate%20TikTok%20once%20he%20takes%20office%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20message%20added.%20%26quot%3BPlease%20stay%20tuned!%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20months%20of%20legal%20tussles%2C%20the%20US%20Supreme%20Court%20on%20Friday%20upheld%20a%20law%20that%20would%20ban%20the%20popular%20video-sharing%20platform%20in%20the%20name%20of%20national%20security%2C%20unless%20its%20Chinese%20owners%20reach%20a%20deal%20to%20sell%20it%20to%20non-Chinese%20buyers%20by%20Sunday.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFrom%20teenage%20dancers%20to%20grandmothers%20sharing%20cooking%20tips%2C%20TikTok%20has%20been%20embraced%20for%20its%20ability%20to%20transform%20ordinary%20users%20into%20global%20celebrities%20when%20a%20video%20goes%20viral.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20also%20has%20a%20fan%20in%20Trump%2C%20who%20has%20credited%20the%20app%20with%20connecting%20him%20to%20younger%20voters%2C%20contributing%20to%20his%20election%20victory%20in%20November.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20discussing%20TikTok%20with%20Chinese%20President%20Xi%20Jinping%2C%20Trump%20told%20NBC%20News%20on%20Saturday%20that%20he%20could%20activate%20a%2090-day%20reprieve%20after%20he%20reclaims%20the%20Oval%20Office.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20think%20that%20would%20be%2C%20certainly%2C%20an%20option%20that%20we%20look%20at.%20The%2090-day%20extension%20is%20something%20that%20will%20be%20most%20likely%20done%2C%20because%20it's%20appropriate%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said%2C%20ahead%20of%20Monday's%20inauguration.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIf%20I%20decide%20to%20do%20that%2C%20I'll%20probably%20announce%20it%20on%20Monday.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20law%20allows%20a%2090-day%20delay%20if%20the%20White%20House%20can%20show%20progress%20toward%20a%20viable%20deal%2C%20but%20TikTok%20owner%20ByteDance%20has%20flatly%20refused%20any%20sale.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20administration%20of%20outgoing%20President%20Joe%20Biden%20has%20said%20it%20will%20leave%20the%20matter%20to%20Trump%2C%20and%20White%20House%20spokeswoman%20Karine%20Jean-Pierre%20qualified%20TikTok's%20latest%20statements%20as%20a%20%26quot%3Bstunt.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20the%20court%20defeat%2C%20TikTok%20CEO%20Shou%20Chew%20appealed%20to%20Trump%2C%20thanking%20him%20for%20his%20%26quot%3Bcommitment%20to%20work%20with%20us%20to%20find%20a%20solution.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETrump%20%26quot%3Btruly%20understands%20our%20platform%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EChew%20is%20also%20set%20to%20attend%20Trump's%20inauguration%20on%20Monday.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20law%20requires%20Apple%20and%20Google%20to%20remove%20TikTok%20from%20their%20app%20stores%2C%20blocking%20new%20downloads.%20The%20companies%20could%20face%20penalties%20of%20up%20to%20%245%2C000%20per%20user%20who%20can%20access%20the%20app.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOracle%2C%20which%20hosts%20TikTok's%20servers%2C%20would%20also%20be%20legally%20obligated%20to%20enforce%20the%20ban.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENone%20of%20the%20companies%20responded%20to%20requests%20for%20comment%20on%20Saturday.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EOffers%20for%20TikTok%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20last-minute%20proposal%20made%20Saturday%20by%20the%20highly-valued%20start-up%20Perplexity%20AI%20offered%20a%20merger%20with%20the%20US%20subsidiary%20of%20TikTok%2C%20a%20source%20with%20knowledge%20of%20the%20deal%20told%20AFP.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThat%20deal%20could%20allow%20parent%20company%20ByteDance%20a%20possible%20solution%20without%20selling%20off%20the%20app%20entirely.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20plan%2C%20first%20reported%20by%20US%20broadcaster%20CNBC%2C%20would%20create%20a%20new%20joint%20venture%20combining%20the%20assets%20of%20US%20TikTok%20and%20Perplexity%20AI%2C%20which%20has%20been%20backed%20by%20Amazon%20founder%20Jeff%20Bezos.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20proposal%20did%20not%20include%20a%20price%20for%20the%20transaction%2C%20but%20the%20source%20estimated%20it%20would%20be%20at%20least%20%2450%20billion.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFrank%20McCourt%2C%20the%20former%20Los%20Angeles%20Dodgers%20owner%2C%20has%20also%20made%20an%20offer%20to%20purchase%20TikTok's%20US%20activity%20and%20said%20he's%20%26quot%3Bready%20to%20work%20with%20the%20company%20and%20President%20Trump%20to%20complete%20a%20deal.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECanadian%20investor%20Kevin%20O'Leary%2C%20who%20is%20involved%20in%20that%20offer%2C%20told%20Fox%20News%20that%20ByteDance%20was%20offered%20%2420%20billion%20for%20TikTok's%20US%20operation.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20acknowledged%20the%20legal%20uncertainty%20over%20the%20case%2C%20with%20it%20remaining%20an%20open%20question%20whether%20an%20executive%20order%20by%20Trump%20to%20halt%20the%20ban%20would%20override%20the%20law.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BCongress%20wrote%20this%20law%20to%20be%20virtually%20president-proof%2C%26quot%3B%20warned%20Adam%20Kovacevich%2C%20chief%20executive%20of%20industry%20trade%20group%20Chamber%20of%20Progress.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESarah%20Kreps%2C%20a%20professor%20of%20government%20and%20law%20at%20Cornell%20University%2C%20said%20that%20%26quot%3Bif%20an%20executive%20order%20conflicts%20with%20an%20existing%20law%2C%20the%20law%20takes%20precedence%2C%20and%20the%20order%20can%20be%20struck%20down%20by%20the%20courts.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWith%20TikTok%20forced%20into%20a%20shutdown%2C%20its%20US-based%20rivals%20Instagram%20Reels%20and%20YouTube%20Shorts%20could%20reap%20benefits.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThousands%20of%20worried%20TikTok%20users%20have%20protectively%20turned%20to%20Xiaohongshu%20(%26quot%3BLittle%20Red%20Book%26quot%3B)%2C%20a%20Chinese%20social%20media%20network%20similar%20to%20Instagram.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENicknamed%20%26quot%3BRed%20Note%26quot%3B%20by%20its%20American%20users%2C%20it%20was%20the%20most%20downloaded%20app%20on%20the%20US%20Apple%20Store%20this%20week.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1737260100000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2025-01%2F252kk30g_tiktok_625x300_18_January_25.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Ftiktok-stops-working-for-us-users-ahead-of-federal-ban-7507570%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22%26quot%3BA%20law%20banning%20TikTok%20has%20been%20enacted%20in%20the%20US%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20a%20message%20to%20users%20attempting%20to%20use%20the%