0from%20Nepal%2C%20Suman%20Nepali.%20They%20succumbed%20to%20injuries%20after%20hitting%20rocks%20due%20to%20a%20snapped%20rope.%20The%20owner%20of%20the%20paragliding%20company%20is%20charged%20with%20culpable%20homicide.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22MURARI%20SHETYE%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fcity%2Fgoa%2Fwoman-tourist-instructor-killed-in-paragliding-accident-in-goa%2Farticleshow%2F117365736.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Danish%20Star%20Blasts%20Playing%20Conditions%20At%20India%20Open%20Badminton%3A%20%26quot%3BUnhealthy...%26quot%3B%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EDenmark's%20Mia%20Blichfeldt%20has%20slammed%20the%20playing%20conditions%20at%20the%20Indira%20Gandhi%20Indoor%20Stadium%2C%20which%20is%20hosting%20the%20India%20Open%20Super%20750%20badminton%20tournament%2C%20and%20also%20criticised%20the%20pollution%20levels%20in%20the%20national%20capital%2C%20calling%20such%20conditions%20%26quot%3Bunhealthy%20and%20unacceptable.%26quot%3B%20The%20world%20no.%2023%20had%20picked%20up%20a%20stomach%20infection%20but%20managed%20to%20fight%20through%20the%20second%20round%20before%20losing%2021-13%2016-21%208-21%20to%20China's%20Wang%20Zhi%20Yi.%20%26quot%3BFinally%20home%20after%20a%20long%20and%20stressful%20week%20in%20India.%20It's%202%20years%20in%20a%20row%20now%20that%20I%20get%20sick%20during%20India%20Open%2C%26quot%3B%20Blichfeldt%20wrote%20on%20Instagram.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt's%20really%20hard%20to%20accept%20that%20many%20weeks%20of%20work%20and%20preparing%2C%20gets%20wasted%20because%20of%20bad%20conditions.%20It's%20not%20fair%20to%20anyone%20that%20we%20have%20to%20train%20and%20play%20in%20smog%2C%20birds%20shitting%20on%20the%20courts%2C%20and%20dirt%20everywhere.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThese%20conditions%20are%20too%20unhealthy%20and%20unacceptable.%20%40bwf.official.%20I'm%20happy%20that%20I%20managed%20the%20second%20round%2C%20but%20I'm%20far%20from%20satisfied.%26quot%3B%20The%20Badminton%20Association%20of%20India%20(BAI)%2C%20on%20its%20part%2C%20said%20that%20it%20faced%20%26quot%3Blogistical%20challenges%26quot%3B%20after%20getting%20the%20venue%20just%20four%20days%20before%20the%20event%20and%20it%20is%20looking%20for%20%26quot%3Balternative%20venues%26quot%3B%20to%20host%20the%20iconic%20event.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAs%20the%20host%20and%20staging%20authority%20for%20the%20Yonex%20Sunrise%20India%20Open%2C%20the%20Badminton%20Association%20of%20India%20gains%20access%20to%20the%20stadium%20and%20its%20infrastructure%20only%20four%20days%20before%20the%20event%2C%20which%20poses%20significant%20logistical%20challenges%2C%26quot%3B%20BAI%20secretary%20Sanjay%20Mishra%20said%20in%20a%20statement%20on%20Saturday.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20are%20already%20in%20discussions%20with%20the%20BWF%20to%20explore%20alternative%20venues%20and%20are%20actively%20evaluating%20the%20infrastructure%20options%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFollowing%20her%20loss%20on%20Thursday%2C%20Blichfeldt%20told%20the%20BWF%20media%20team%20that%20she%20had%20thrown%20up%20all%20night%20and%20was%20barely%20able%20to%20get%20on%20the%20court%20the%20next%20day%20for%20her%20second%20round%20match.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThat%20night%20(Tuesday)%20was%20terrible.%20The%20only%20sleep%20I%20got%20was%20in%20the%20morning%20because%20I%20kept%20throwing%20up%20all%20night.%20I'm%20really%20tired%20now%20and%20my%20body%20is%20really%20dead%2C%26quot%3B%20Blichfeldt%20had%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt's%20not%20so%20nice%20for%20me%2C%20but%20I'm%20happy%20with%20the%20match%20I%20pulled%20yesterday%20and%20the%20outcome%20today%20but%20I%20wish%20I%20could%20have%20gone%20to%20court%20at%20100%20per%20cent.%20It%20happened%20Tuesday%20evening.%20It%20took%20a%20lot%20of%20mental%20work%20(to%20get%20on%20court).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt's%20really%20frustrating%20when%20you've%20been%20training%20to%20come%20to%20these%20tournaments%20and%20then%20this%20is%20one%20of%20the%20things%20that%20stops%20you%20from%20performing.%26quot%3B%20French%20mixed%20doubles%20pair%20of%20Thom%20Gicquel%20and%20Delphine%20Delrue%20had%20also%20expressed%20concerns%20about%20the%20weather%20conditions%20on%20Thursday.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20playing%20hall%20is%20pretty%20nice.%20But%20the%20weather%20is%20pretty%20cold%20here%20in%20Delhi%20and%20the%20pollution%20is%20really%20high%20right%20now%2C%20so%20it's%20not%20easy%20to%20play%2C%20not%20the%20best%20conditions%20to%20play%20in%2C%26quot%3B%20Gicquel%20had%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20is%20not%20an%20isolated%20incident%2C%20as%20during%20the%202023%20Syed%20Modi%20International%20Super%20300%20tournament%2C%20foreign%20players%20had%20also%20raised%20concerns%20about%20the%20poor%20conditions%20at%20the%20Babu%20Banarasi%20Das%20Indoor%20Stadium%2C%20citing%20issues%20such%20as%20bird%20droppings%20and%20dust-laden%20courts.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20few%20days%20later%2C%20Malaysian%20Soong%20Joo%20Ven%20took%20to%20social%20media%20to%20complain%20about%20muddy%20brown%20water%20leaking%20from%20a%20basin%20faucet%20at%20his%20hotel%20upon%20his%20arrival%20in%20Guwahati%20for%20the%20Guwahati%20Masters%20Super%20100.%20Additionally%2C%20former%20world%20number%201%20Nozomi%20Okuhara%20of%20Japan%20claimed%20to%20have%20had%20a%20nightmarish%20experience%20during%20the%20Odisha%20Open%2C%20where%20she%20was%20overcharged%20by%20a%20private%20cabbie%20and%20then%20made%20to%20wait%20for%20more%20than%20four%20hours%20to%20check%20into%20a%20hotel%20in%20Cuttack.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1737254880000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2025-01%2F2l4atan_cs_625x300_19_January_25.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fbadminton%2Fsmog-dirt-danish-star-mia-blichfeldt-blasts-playing-conditions-at-i