r%20Morcha%20(KMM)%2C%20which%20are%20spearheading%20the%20agitation%20for%20the%20last%2011%20months.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFollowing%20the%20announcement%20of%20the%20meeting%20on%20February%2014%2C%20farmer%20leaders%20appealed%20to%20Dallewal%20to%20take%20medical%20aid%20so%20that%20he%20can%20participate%20in%20the%20proposed%20deliberations.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Centre's%20delegation%20also%20urged%20Dallewal%20to%20take%20medical%20aid%20so%20that%20he%20can%20participate%20in%20the%20proposed%20meeting%2C%20which%20will%20take%20place%20at%20the%20Mahatma%20Gandhi%20State%20Institute%20of%20Public%20Administration%20at%20Chandigarh%20at%205%20pm%20on%20February%2014.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETalking%20to%20reporters%20at%20the%20Khanauri%20protest%20site%2C%20Ranjan%20said%20a%20high-level%20delegation%20was%20sent%20by%20the%20Centre%2C%20keeping%20in%20mind%20the%20deteriorating%20health%20of%20Dallewal.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20enquired%20about%20his%20health%20and%20held%20a%20meeting%20with%20the%20representatives%20(of%20the%20protesting%20farmer%20bodies)%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERanjan%20said%20the%20meeting%20will%20be%20held%20in%20Chandigarh%20on%20February%2014.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20urged%20him%20(Dallewal)%20to%20break%20his%20fast%20and%20take%20medical%20aid%2C%20so%20that%20he%20can%20participate%20in%20the%20meeting%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20letter%20addressed%20to%20Dallewal%2C%20SKM%20(Non-Political)%20and%20KMM%20read%3A%20%26quot%3BThis%20is%20in%20continuation%20of%20the%20previous%20meeting%20with%20the%20leaders%20of%20SKM%20(Non-Political)%20and%20Kisan%20Mazdoor%20Morcha%20(KMM)%2C%20which%20was%20held%20on%20February%2015%2C%202024%20at%20Chandigarh.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BA%20meeting%20with%20the%20ministers%20of%20the%20government%20of%20India%20and%20the%20Punjab%20government%20regarding%20the%20demands%20of%20the%20farmers'%20unions%20has%20been%20convened%20on%20February%2014%2C%202025%20(5%20pm)%20at%20the%20Mahatma%20Gandhi%20State%20Institute%20of%20Public%20Administration%20Punjab%20(MGSIPA)%2C%20Sector-26%2C%20Chandigarh.%20You%20are%20cordially%20invited%20to%20the%20meeting%2C%20please%20attend%20at%20the%20scheduled%20time.%20We%20hope%20that%20Dallewal%20will%20soon%20end%20his%20fast%2C%20recover%20and%20join%20the%20discussion%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20the%20letter%20written%20by%20Ranjan.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFour%20rounds%20of%20meetings%20had%20taken%20place%20between%20Union%20ministers%20and%20the%20protesting%20farmers%20on%20February%208%2C%2012%2C%2015%20and%2018%20last%20year%2C%20but%20the%20talks%20remained%20inconclusive.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEarlier%20on%20Saturday%2C%20the%20farmers%20protesting%20at%20the%20Khanauri%20and%20Shambhu%20border%20points%20between%20Punjab%20and%20Haryana%20said%20they%20have%20received%20a%20proposal%20from%20the%20central%20government%20which%20they%20will%20discuss.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Centre's%20delegation%20held%20meetings%20with%20the%20representatives%20of%20both%20the%20forums.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20Punjab%20government%20team%20led%20by%20retired%20additional%20director%20general%20of%20police%20Jaskaran%20Singh%20and%20former%20deputy%20inspector%20general%20of%20police%20Narinder%20Bhargav%2C%20who%20were%20holding%20discussions%20with%20the%20farmer%20leaders%2C%20was%20also%20present.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20farmer%20leader%20Abhimanyu%20Kohar%2C%20officials%20have%20said%20February%2014%20has%20been%20fixed%20for%20the%20meeting%20as%20Assembly%20polls%20are%20due%20in%20Delhi%20and%20the%20Model%20Code%20of%20Conduct%20will%20be%20in%20force%20in%20the%20capital%20till%20February%209.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhen%20the%20Model%20Code%20of%20Conduct%20is%20in%20force%2C%20no%20government%20can%20make%20any%20announcement%2C%20Kohar%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESharing%20details%20about%20Dallewal's%20health%2C%20Kohar%20said%20the%20farmer%20leader%20was%20unable%20to%20take%20water%20and%20had%20been%20vomiting.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDoctors%20have%20warned%20that%20anything%20could%20happen%20to%20Dallewal%2C%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBefore%20agreeing%20to%20take%20medical%20aid%2C%20Dallewal%20had%20asked%20the%20farmer%20leaders%20to%20take%20consent%20from%20the%20121%20farmers%20who%20were%20also%20on%20an%20indefinite%20fast.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20few%20days%20ago%2C%20a%20group%20of%20111%20farmers%20and%20later%2C%2010%20more%20farmers%20sat%20on%20a%20fast-unto-death%20in%20solidarity%20with%20Dallewal.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDallewal%2C%20who%20is%20the%20convenor%20of%20the%20SKM%20(Non-Political)%2C%20has%20been%20on%20an%20indefinite%20hunger%20strike%20at%20the%20Khanauri%20border%20point%20since%20November%2026%20last%20year%20in%20support%20of%20various%20demands%2C%20including%20a%20legal%20guarantee%20on%20the%20MSP%20for%20crops.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFarmers%20had%20said%20Dallewal%20had%20not%20eaten%20anything%20since%20November%2026%20last%20year%20and%20was%20just%20surviving%20on%20water.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFarmer%20leaders%20on%20Thursday%20said%20Dallewal%20has%20lost%20about%2020-kg%20weight%20during%20his%20fast-unto-death.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20weight%20of%20Dallewal%20has%20reduced%20to%2066.4%20kg%20now%20from%2086.9%20kg%2C%20when%20he%20began%20the%20indefinite%20fast.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFarmers%2C%20under%20the%20banner%20of%20the%20SKM%20(Non-Political)%20and%20KMM%2C%20have%20been%20camping%20at%20the%20Shambhu%20and%20Khanauri%20border%20points%20since%20February%2013%20last%20year%2C%20after%20security%20forces%20did%20not%20allow%20them%20to%20march%20to%20Delhi%20to%20press%20for%20their%20various%20demands%2C%20including%20a%20legal%20guarantee%20on%20the%20MSP%20for%20their%20crops.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%20a%20syn