%20invite%20my%20in-laws%20on%20family%20vacations%20but%20I%20don't%20regret%20it.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EMy%20children%20get%20to%20see%20a%20can-do%2C%20adventurous%20attitude%20modeled%20by%20their%20grandparents.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3ETraveling%20together%20has%20many%20benefits%2C%20including%20shared%20memories%20and%20built-in%20babysitting.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3ESeveral%20years%20ago%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fi-was-against-cruises-going-with-kids-changed-my-mind-2022-7%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Emy%20husband%20and%20I%20invited%20his%20parents%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20take%20an%20eight-day%20trip%20to%20Montana%20and%20Wyoming%20with%20us%20and%20our%20two%20children.%20I%20worried%20eight%20days%20could%20be%20too%20long%20to%20spend%20together%20in%20confined%3Cstrong%3E%3Cem%3E%20%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fstrong%3Espaces%2C%20especially%20with%20a%204%20and%209-year-old.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWe%20went%20for%20it%20anyway.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMy%20in-laws%20jumped%20at%20the%20opportunity%20to%20spend%20extended%20time%20with%20their%20grandkids.%20The%20trip%20had%20only%20minor%20hiccups%20%E2%80%94%20whining%20and%20little%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmy-6-year-old-only-has-tantrums-around-his-grandparents-2022-11%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Emeltdowns%20from%20the%20children%3C%2Fa%3E%20%E2%80%94%20but%20it%20went%20so%20smoothly%20that%20we've%20invited%20my%20in-laws%20on%20every%20family%20vacation%20since.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThis%20year%20marked%20our%2010th%20trip%20with%20the%20abuelitos%20(grandparents).%20Here's%20what%20we've%20learned.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2232429a99-eb23-44d9-8a43-88971d8da33a%5C%22%3ESpending%20time%20together%20strengthens%20our%20bond%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3ERiding%20for%20five-%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhonda-pilot-vs-hyundai-palisade-review-family-suv-compared-2024-12%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E10-hour%20stints%20in%20an%20SUV%3C%2Fa%3E%20has%20promoted%20heart-to-heart%20conversations%20with%20my%20mother-in-law%20about%20her%20family%20and%20childhood%20that%20I'm%20not%20sure%20we%20would%20have%20heard%20otherwise.%20Thanks%20to%20these%20long%2C%20uninterrupted%20hours%2C%20we%20know%20she%20grew%20up%20in%20a%20one-bedroom%20house%20in%20Mesa%2C%20Arizona%2C%20with%20five%20of%20her%20nine%20siblings%2C%20a%20backyard%20garden%2C%20and%20the%20chickens%20they%20raised%20to%20eat.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThese%20trips%20have%20also%20revealed%20another%20side%20of%20my%20father-in-law.%20He's%20quiet%20by%20nature%20but%20my%20husband%20and%20I%20discovered%20he%20loves%20meeting%20new%20people.%20In%20a%20jacuzzi%20in%20Jackson%20Hole%2C%20we%20listened%20to%20him%20crack%20jokes%20and%20engage%20in%20small%20talk%20with%20other%20retirees.%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Factivities-tourists-cant-miss-in-mexico-city-cdmx-local-tips-2023-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EOutside%20of%20Mexico%20City%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20he%20befriended%20a%20man%20who%20grew%20up%20in%20the%20same%20region%20of%20Mexico%20as%20he%20did.%20The%20two%20shared%20tales%20of%20a%20Quinta%20(large%20estate)%20that%20housed%20exotic%20animals%20and%20the%20area's%20best%20watering%20holes.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETraveling%20together%20has%20forged%20a%20deeper%20understanding%20of%20each%20other%20and%20our%20roots.%20And%20although%20it's%20fun%20to%20reflect%20on%20the%20past%2C%20these%20trips%20also%20provide%20opportunities%20to%20create%20new%20narratives.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22ef2bb5a4-fd3e-4d51-9362-c35158c69a2d%5C%22%3EOur%20children%20build%20memories%20with%20their%20grandparents%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BRemember%20that%20time%20we%E2%80%A6%26quot%3B%20begins%20many%20of%20our%20conversations.%20It's%20one%20of%20the%20best%20parts%20of%20taking%20vacations%20together.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI'm%20glad%20we%20invited%20my%20in-laws%20on%20trips%20when%20the%20kids%20were%20young%2C%20even%20if%20whining%20and%20tantrums%20happened.%20If%20we'd%20waited%20for%20our%20kids%20to%20be%20a%20more%20%26quot%3Bideal%20age%2C%26quot%3B%20my%20in-laws%20would%20have%20been%20older%20and%20some%20of%20those%20trips%20to%20far-off%20places%20may%20not%20have%20happened%20had%20we%20waited.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESometimes%20my%20children%20pull%20out%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fguides%2Fgifts%2Fbest-photo-books%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eour%20travel%20albums%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20point%20to%20photos%20with%20their%20grandparents%20in%20front%20of%20a%20geyser%20or%20a%20historical%20site.%20These%20memories%20are%20priceless.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMy%20husband%20and%20I%20enjoy%20introducing%20his%20parents%20to%20places%20and%20activities%20outside%20their%20comfort%20zone.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMy%20husband%20and%20I%20have%20encouraged%20my%20in-laws%20to%20hike%20or%20crawl%20into%20caves%20with%20us.%20We've%20so%20often%20pushed%20them%20past%20their%20boundaries%20that%20my%20mother-in-law%20admits%20they%20start%20a%20walking%20regimen%20months%20before%20our%20trips%20to%20prepare%20for%20whatever%20nonsense%20I%20plan.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20love%20that%20they%20can%20count%20on%20us%20for%20an%20adventure%2C%20and%20I'm%20always%20impressed%20at%20their%20willing%20attitude.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMy%20father-in-law's%20favorite%20part%20of%20our%20trip%20to%20Yellowstone%20was%20the%201.5-mile%20out-and-back%20hike%20to%20the%20Grand%20Prismatic%20Spring.%20With%20a%20gradual%20105-foot%20climb%2C%20he%20huffed%20and%20puffed%20up%20that%20trail%20and%20nearly%20gave%20up%20until%20a%20couple%20older%20than%20passed%20him%20on%20the%20path%2C%20calling%20out%2C%20%26quot%3BYou've%20got%20this!%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20said%20their%20words%20bolstered%20him%20and%20the%20Prismatic%20Spring%20view%20was%20worth%20the%20effort.%20Similarly%2C%20at%20the%20Teotihicuan%20Pyramids%20outside%20Mexico%20City%2C%20my%20mother-in-law%20found%20the%20steep%2C%20narrow%20climb%20nearly%20impossible.%20But%20she%20said%20the%20experience%20of%20standing%20on%20ancient%20stones%20and%20overlooking%20the%20plaza%20was%20unforgettable.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EUnconsciously%2C%20but%20powerfully%2C%20my%20children's%20abuelitos%20are%20modeling%20a%20%26quot%3Bcan-do%20attitude%26quot%3B%20to%20them%20and%20that%20it's%20never%20too%20late%20to%20try%20new%20things%20and%20embrace%20adventure.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBesides%20the%20inward%20gains%20of%20traveling%20together%2C%20there%20are%20also%20practical%20benefits.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2269ed2e59-2ab7-4a5e-866d-0ff4612eb068%5C%22%3ETraveling%20in%20a%20group%20is%20more%20economical%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EWe%20always%20look%20for%20Airbnbs%20or%20hotels%20that%20accommodate%20a%20party%20of%20seven.%20We%20rent%20vans%20or%20SUVs%2C%20allowing%20us%20to%20split%20the%20cost%20of%20a%20rental%20vehicle%2C%20making%20one%20of%20the%20most%20expensive%20items%20on%20a%20travel%20budget%20more%20economical.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAdmittedly%2C%20this%20works%20more%20in%20our%20favor%20than%20theirs%2C%20but%20I%20appreciate%20it%20when%20they%20also%20offer%20to%20split%20a%20meal%20with%20us%20or%20add%20one%20of%20the%20kid's%20meals%20to%20their%20tab.%20Meals%20out%20are%20expensive%20and%20their%20willingness%20to%20share%20some%20of%20that%20cost%20means%20our%20family%20can%20better%20afford%20travel.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAnother%20practical%20aspect%20of%20traveling%20that%20benefits%20us%20is%20the%20free%20babysitting%20my%20husband%20and%20I%20receive.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22554ce90a-2e48-4156-8bc0-8e4327f4c800%5C%22%3EGrandparents%20can%20be%20the%20best%20built-in%20babysitters%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3ETraveling%20with%20three%20kids%20has%20its%20challenges.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOn%20our%20last%20trip%2C%20my%20husband%20and%20I%20were%20so%20worn%20out%20from%20two%20long%20adventure%20days%20that%20we%20needed%20a