rbon%20%26amp%3B%20Whale.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESiddharth%20says%20they%20focussed%20on%20collaborating%20with%20local%20schools%20to%20encourage%20students%20to%20bring%20segregated%20plastic%20waste%20from%20home%2C%20which%20they%20creatively%20transform%20into%20items%20like%20plant%20pots%2C%20earrings%2C%20and%20keychains.%20He%20explains%20that%20the%20idea%20of%20focusing%20on%20schoolchildren%20stems%20from%20the%20belief%20that%20they%20are%20the%20seeds%20of%20our%20future%2C%20adding%2C%20%E2%80%9CNurturing%20them%20with%20the%20right%20values%20will%20shape%20a%20better%20tomorrow.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMeanwhile%2C%20talking%20about%20the%20distinctive%20features%20of%20their%20products%2C%20Alvin%20says%2C%20%E2%80%9CThe%20paver%20tile%20has%20more%20strength%20than%20a%20normal%20interlock%20made%20of%20concrete.%20This%20is%20one%20of%20our%20USPs%20(Unique%20Selling%20Point).%20There%20is%20also%20no%20issue%20of%20wear%20and%20tear%20or%20rusting%2C%20which%20is%20common%20in%20metal%20benches.%20If%20anything%20happens%20to%20the%20recycled%20material%2C%20we%20can%20recycle%20it%20again.%20As%20these%20are%20made%20of%20plastic%2C%20they%20are%20durable%20and%20protected%20from%20termite%20damage%2C%20unlike%20wooden%20furniture.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETheir%20interlock%20paver%20tiles%20and%20public%20benches%20have%20already%20been%20installed%20in%20several%20malls%20and%20metro%20stations%20across%20Kerala%20and%20Bengaluru.%20Interestingly%2C%20the%20friends%20have%20partnered%20with%20LuLu%20Group%2C%20HiLITE%20group%2C%20Cochin%20Smart%20Mission%20Limited%20(CSML)%2C%20Malabar%20Group%2C%20Centre%20Square%20Mall%20Kochi%2C%20Kochi%20Metro%2C%20and%20Kerala%20Tourism.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Clabel%3EAdvertisement%3C%2Flabel%3E%5Cn%3Cins%20data-ad-slot%3D%5C%224678180483%5C%22%20data-ad-client%3D%5C%22ca-pub-5691287967087057%5C%22%20data-ad-format%3D%5C%22fluid%5C%22%20data-ad-layout%3D%5C%22i