network%20of%2050%2C000%20ragpickers%20across%20states%2C%20including%20Tamil%20Nadu%2C%20Andhra%20Pradesh%2C%20Karnataka%2C%20Kerala%2C%20and%20Puducherry.%20The%20bottles%20are%20carefully%20sorted%2C%20and%20any%20caps%2C%20wrappers%2C%20or%20contaminants%20are%20removed.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fol%3E%5Cn%3Col%20start%3D%5C%222%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-list%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3E%3Cstrong%3ECrushing%20and%20flaking%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20Once%20cleaned%2C%20the%20PET%20bottles%20are%20crushed%20into%20small%20flakes%2C%20typically%20three%20to%20eight%20millimetres%20in%20size.%20This%20step%20reduces%20the%20material%20to%20a%20manageable%20form%20that%20can%20easily%20be%20processed%20into%20new%20products.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fol%3E%5Cn%3Col%20start%3D%5C%223%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-list%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3E%3Cstrong%3EMelting%20and%20spinning%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20The%20PET%20flakes%20are%20melted%20at%20300%C2%B0C%20using%20an%20extruder.%20The%20molten%20material%20is%20then%20stretched%20to%20form%20polyester%20fibre%2C%20which%20is%20cooled%20and%20transformed%20into%20yarn.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3E%3Cstrong%3EWeaving%20the%20fabric%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20The%20yarn%20is%20then%20woven%20into%20fabric%2C%20forming%20the%20foundation%20for%20the%20clothing%20line.%20This%20fabric%20is%20then%20tailored%20into%20products%20such%20as%20jackets%2C%20T-shirts%2C%20and%20blazers.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fol%3E%5Cn%3Col%20start%3D%5C%225%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-list%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3E%3Cstrong%3EWaterless%20dyeing%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20One%20of%20the%20key%20innovations%20at%20EcoLine%20is%20the%20use%20of%20dope%20dye%20technology.%20Instead%20of%20dyeing%20the%20fabric%20after%20it%E2%80%99s%20made%20%E2%80%94%20a%20traditional%20process%20that%20consumes%20vast%20amounts%20of%20water%20%E2%80%94%20EcoLine%20infuses%20the%20colour%20directly%20into%20the%20polyester%20fibre%20during%20its%20production.%20This%20unique%20process%20eliminates%20the%20need%20for%20