0Ferns%E2%80%99%20Pickles%20stays%20true%20to%20its%20moral%20compass%20of%20business%2C%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F302505%2Fjodhpur-couple-grow-organic-exotic-vegetables-on-ancestral-land-mharokhet-experiential-farm%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eprocuring%20its%20vegetables%20and%20fruits%20from%20farms%20%3C%2Fa%3Earound%20the%20factory%20in%20Pune.%20The%20preserves%20are%20prepared%20within%2024%20hours%20of%20harvest.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBrian%20accompanies%20the%20virtual%20tour%20of%20the%20factory%20with%20the%20story%20of%20how%20the%20business%20reins%20passed%20on%20to%20him.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAt%20just%2017%20years%20of%20age%2C%20he%20was%20entrusted%20with%20the%20legacy%20of%20Ferns%E2%80%99%20Pickles%20following%20the%20demise%20of%20his%20father%20George%20who%20was%20charge%20d%E2%80%99affaires%20after%20Nataline%20passed%20away%20in%201966.%20He%20spent%20the%20next%20several%20years%20ensuring%20he%20did%20justice%20to%20his%20role.%20The%20fully%20automated%20factory%20with%20BRC%20(British%20Retail%20Consortium)%20certification%20%E2%80%94%20an%20international%20mark%20of%20excellence%20%E2%80%94%20is%20proof.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20he%20assures%2C%20%E2%80%9CThe%20factory%20is%20fully%20automated%20but%20the%20recipes%20we%20follow%20are%20traditional.%20They%20are%20all%20my%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F359191%2Fparsi-food-in-mumbai-cloud-kitchen-farida-nanavaty-karrylicious-dhansak-laga-nu-custard-prawn-patia%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Egrandmother%E2%80%99s%20originals%3C%2Fa%3E.%E2%80%9D%20Drawing%20on%20the%20point%20of%20the%20brand%E2%80%99s%20consistency%2C%20their%20loyalists%20span%20the%20globe.%20%E2%80%9CIf%20you%20go%20to%20any%20Chinese%20restaurant%20in%20the%20UK%20and%20have%20the%20noodles%2C%20it%20is%20guaranteed%20to%20be%20made%20of%20Ferns%E2%80%99%20curry%20paste.%20We%20even%20supply%20to%20the%20Japanese%20restaurant%20chain%20in%20the%20UK%2C%20Wagamama.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22auto%2C%20(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F01%2Fpickle-business-Ferns-Pickles-3-1735899444.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20new%20factory%20in%20Pune%20is%20home%20to%20a%20thriving%20farmland%20ensuring%20that%20the%20preserves%20are%20prepared%20from%20the%20freshest%20of%20produce%20%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F01%2Fpickle-business-Ferns-Pickles-3-1735899444.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F01%2Fpickle-business-Ferns-Pickles-3-1735899444-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F01%2Fpickle-business-Ferns-Pickles-3-1735899444-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F01%2Fpickle-business-Ferns-Pickles-3-1735899444-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F01%2Fpickle-business-Ferns-Pickles-3-1735899444-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-395105%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EThe%20new%20factory%20in%20Pune%20is%20home%20to%20a%20thriving%20farmland%20ensuring%20that%20the%20preserves%20are%20prepared%20from%20the%20freshest%20produce%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20today%2C%20Ferns%E2%80%99%20pickles%20and%20curry%20pastes%20are%20exported%20to%20Canada%2C%20USA%2C%20Australia%20and%20New%20Zealand%2C%20it%20isn%E2%80%99t%20the%20first%20time%20the%20brand%20is%20getting%20global%20love.%20Again%2C%20Nataline%20was%20way%20ahead%20of%20the%20curve%20when%20it%20came%20to%20marketing.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%201947%2C%20when%20the%20last%20of%20the%20British%20were%20leaving%20the%20country%2C%20disappointed%20that%20they%20would%20have%20to%20forego%20their%20delicious%20pickles%20and%20jams%2C%20Nataline%20managed%20to%20find%20a%20Mumbai-based%20merchant%20exporter%20who%20agreed%20to%20carry%20her%20pickles%20to%20the%20UK%20in%201949%20%E2%80%94%20thus%20laying%20the%20carpet%20for%20export%20opportunities.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F345161%2Ftvaran-by-cisco-villgro-empower-women-led-startups-female-entrepreneurs-climate-action%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EBuilding%20a%20business%20as%20a%20woman%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20the%201920s%2C%20required%20a%20certain%20level%20of%20intrepidity.%20And%20Nataline%20left%20no%20stone%20unturned.%20Brian%20shares%2C%20%E2%80%9CMy%20grandmother%20used%20to%20work%20really%20hard.%20In%20those%20days%2C%20Pune%20was%20mostly%20jungle%20land.%20So%2C%20she%20would%20cycle%20to%20the%20market%20at%204.30%20am%20to%20buy%20the%20ingredients%20she%20needed%20and%20put%20it%20on%20a%20bullock%20cart%2C%20which%20would%20then%20bring%20it%20back%20to%20the%20factory%20to%20be%20cooked%20and%20processed.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShe%20would%20meticulously%20record%20her%20recipes%20in%20a%20book%2C%20a%20sort%20of%20archive%20of%20food%20memories%2C%20which%20the%20family%20still%20holds%20on%20to.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3ECarrying%20on%20an%20alimentary%20legacy%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFerns%E2%80%99%20Pickles%20has%20seen%20three%20generations%20of%20expertise.%20And%20Brian%20sees%20this%20as%20a%20testament%20to%20the%20brand%E2%80%99s%20legacy.%20The%20secret%2C%20he%20says%2C%20lies%20in%20continuously%20pushing%20the%20envelope%2C%20a%20trait%20he%20picked%20up%20from%20his%20father%20George.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWhen%20my%20grandmother%20wasn%E2%80%99t%20well%20in%201960%2C%20my%20father%2C%20who%20was%20in%20the%20merchant%20navy%20at%20the%20time%2C%20quit%20and%20took%20over%20the%20business.%20In%20the%2070s%2C%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F263689%2Findia-nilons-pickles-iconic-brands-suresh-prafful-sanghavi-inspiring%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Epickle%20bottles%3C%2Fa%3E%20would%20be%20wrapped%20in%20straw%20and%20put%20into%20wooden%20boxes%20and%20exported.%20But%20the%20journey%20through%20the%20sea%20would%20cause%20the%20bottles%20to%20break.%20My%20father%20was%20one%20of%20the%20first%20to%20start%20using%20cardboard%20boxes%20for%20packaging.%20This%20sorted%20the%20issue%20of%20breakage.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22auto%2C%20(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F01%2Fpickle-business-Ferns-Pickles-4-1735899560.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22All%20the%20processes%20at%20the%20new%20factory%20are%20automated%2C%20ensuring%20precision%20and%20consistency%20in%20the%20preserve%20making%20process%20%20%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F01%2Fpickle-business-Ferns-Pickles-4-1735899560.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F01%2Fpickle-business-Ferns-Pickles-4-1735899560-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F01%2Fpickle-business-Ferns-Pickles-4-1735899560-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F01%2Fpickle-business-Ferns-Pickles-4-1735899560-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F01%2Fpickle-business-Ferns-Pickles-4-1735899560-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-395107%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-