2fluid%5C%22%20data-ad-layout%3D%5C%22in-article%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CA%20key%20objective%20of%20the%20movement%20was%20to%20liberate%20future%20generations%20from%20the%20constraints%20of%20caste-based%20occupations%2C%20emphasising%20the%20importance%20of%20education%2C%E2%80%9D%20shares%20Manimaran.%20This%20principle%20was%20demonstrated%20at%20the%20Kathaaiyee%20Amman%20temple%20festival%20in%20Cuddalore.%20When%20local%20parai%20artists%20refused%20to%20participate%2C%20defying%20the%20very%20essence%20of%20the%20movement%2C%20artists%20from%20outside%20the%20region%20were%20brought%20in.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20blatant%20disregard%20for%20the%20community%E2%80%99s%20struggle%20led%20to%20violent%20clashes%2C%20resulting%20in%20the%20tragic%20death%20of%20a%20young%20man%20named%20Reddiyur%20Pandian%20on%20August%2015%2C%201987.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20movement%20was%20an%20eye-opener%20for%20many%2C%20including%20Manimaran%2C%20who%20understood%20the%20difference%20between%20picking%20an%20art%20form%20out%20of%20choice%20and%20picking%20it%20because%20that%20is%20the%20only%20thing%20he%20should%20do.%20%E2%80%9CNobody%20from%20the%20upper%20class%20came%20forward%20to%20play%20parai%2C%20and%20that%E2%80%99s%20because%20parai%E2%80%99s%20art%20status%20was%20not%20satisfactory%20for%20this%20hierarchical%20society%2C%E2%80%9D%20avers%20Manimaran.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EManimaran%2C%20and%20several%20others%20like%20him%2C%20are%20focusing%20on%20the%20correct%20usage%20of%20parai%20%E2%80%94%20an%20instrument%20of%20social%20change%20and%20awareness.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EBreaking%20the%20caste%20barrier%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EToday%2C%20the%20parai%20has%20reclaimed%20its%20dignity%20and%20earned%20a%20better%20platform%20to%20contribute%20to%20societal%20causes.%20%E2%80%9CWe%20use%20parai%20to%20educate%20people%20and%20create%20awareness%20on%20pressing%20societal%20issues%2C%20training%20them%20for%20the%20same%2C%E2%80%9D%20shares%20Manimaran%2C%20who%20founded%20%E2%80%98Buddhar%20Kalai%20Kuzhu%E2%80%99%20%E2%80%94%20an%20academy%20teaching%20parai%20for%20all%20%E2%80%94%20since%202010.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CChange%20has%20to%20come%20within%20the%20parai%20community%20for%20them%20to%20expect%20better%20treatment%20from%20society%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Srinivas%2C%20who%20discourages%20his%20students%20from%20playing%20at%20funerals%20and%20making%20them%20take%20an%20oath%20while%20they%20are%20enrolled%20for%20the%20classes.%20%E2%80%9CWe%20also%20ask%20people%20not%20to%20touch%20the%20parai%20if%20they%20have%20consumed%20alcohol%2C%E2%80%9D%20adds%20Manimaran.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBuddhar%20Kalai%20Koodam%20aims%20to%20promote%20parai%20without%20the%20filter%20of%20oppression%20and%20caste.%20At%20the%20same%20time%2C%20Manimaran%20uses%20parai%20as%20a%20mechanism%20to%20propagate%20the%20importance%20of%20education%2C%20especially%20among%20children%20from%20marginalised%20communities.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-gallery%20wp-block-gallery-3%20wp-block-gallery-is-layout-flex%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F12%2FMervin-Feature-image-10-1734932966.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20group%20of%20women%20playing%20parai%5C%22%20data-id%3D%5C%22391641%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F12%2FMervin-Feature-image-10-1734932966.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F12%2FMervin-Feature-image-10-1734932966-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F12%2FMervin-Feature-image-10-1734932966-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F12%2F