0some%20of%20the%20community%20members.%20It%E2%80%99s%20not%20an%20interview%20where%20I%20meet%20them%20and%20then%20I%20go%20away.%20We%20become%20friends%2C%20we%20share%20space%20and%20ideas%2C%20and%20we%20collaborate%20for%20months%2C%20sometimes%20years.%E2%80%9D%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EChanging%20perspectives%20mid-journey%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMalaika%E2%80%99s%20work%20is%20often%20shaped%20by%20the%20need%20to%20adapt%20to%20the%20ever-evolving%20realities%20on%20the%20ground.%20The%20path%20from%20research%20to%20film%20is%20rarely%20linear%2C%20especially%20when%20the%20stories%20she%20is%20uncovering%20challenge%20preconceived%20notions%20and%20demand%20a%20deeper%2C%20more%20nuanced%20approach.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIt%20happens%20all%20the%20time%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20says%2C%20reflecting%20on%20the%20fluidity%20of%20the%20storytelling%20process.%20%E2%80%9CWe%20did%20a%20story%20about%20traditional%20medicine%20and%20its%20impact%20on%20wildlife%2C%20and%20we%20went%20into%20it%20thinking%20that%20the%20demand%20was%20rooted%20in%20tradition.%E2%80%9D%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhat%20she%20discovered%20in%20Guangzhou%2C%20China%2C%20was%20far%20more%20complex.%20While%20traditional%20Chinese%20medicine%20(TCM)%20was%20part%20of%20the%20equation%2C%20the%20real%20driver%20was%20a%20booming%20business%20demand%2C%20marketing%20the%20medicine%20as%20%E2%80%9Ctraditional%E2%80%9D%20to%20appeal%20to%20consumers.%20This%20revelation%20shifted%20the%20direction%20of%20her%20film%20and%20deepened%20her%20understanding%20of%20the%20forces%20driving%20wildlife%20decimation.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESimilarly%2C%20when%20she%20began%20working%20on%20%3Cem%3ESacrifice%20Zone%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20she%20set%20out%20to%20focus%20on%20environmental%20pollution%20in%20Asia%20%E2%80%94%20specifically%20in%20India%2C%20Bangladesh%2C%20and%20Mongolia.%20But%20after%20shooting%20the%20first%20segment%20in%20Delhi%2C%20she%20was